review: always come back to this classic
this was a brilliant rts for the time it was made and i still have fond nostalgia for when i originally played the game definitely one of the best storylines for an age of empires game
i have played this since it released aside from childhood nostalgia it is a fun engaging game
an amazing classic that is always worth replaying
havent got to playing it again after buying but this is one of my favourites purely because i am more interested in mythologies than empires cant wait to beat the singleplayer campaign once again
